data.description: Gorgeous open concept home that has just been beautifully renovated! This home boasts high ceilings, new upscale laminate flooring throughout entire home, fresh interior and exterior paint, brand new upgraded LG stainless appliances, new lighting, new fence, sprinkler system, a huge master bedroom with walk in closet and covered front and back sitting porches. This home is ready to move in and relax! Fantastic location in close proximity to I-35 and Randolph AFB, major retailers and many restaurants. Located within a sought after school district.
